    "date": "2020-07-01T17:58:01Z",
    "text": "Essential Pay for Essential Workers Act\n\nThis bill requires employers to pay essential health care employees a premium amount in addition to their regular rate of pay during an emergency period. It also allows employers a payroll tax credit for the payment of such enhanced wages to essential employees."
